    • getSessionsRangeByUserId

      List<Session> getSessionsRangeByUserId(String userId, Date from, Date to)
      Returns sessions range for user by user id. Where the range is given by two dates FROM and TO inclusive.
      The method compares session login date.
      Parameters:
      userId - - user id for finding this user into user sessions history db.
      from - - start date of range.
      to - - end date of range.
      Returns:
      List of Session objects.
